The night is storming. Lighting is hitting here and there. On top a 
moutain sits a tree. On top a tree is a giant Crow on a branch. the 
crow opens his mouth "cawwww where is everyone" The Crow land on top 
of a rock "Bot mode" His wings fold into arms, he has a orange head 
and body cover with black feathers. "Message to all bots. Listen up I 
am the CROW LORD hear me CAWWWW" CROW LORD hears a noise behind him. 
he turns around and fires his gun. nailing a bunny right between the 
eyes. "don't do that" he looks around. "beast mode" He turns back to
a 
crow and flies into the sky. 

"CAWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW"
